Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:13.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,髮旋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:22.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？朝倉？大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,不久他就會來迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:46.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:49.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
